text:
The robot tray collector is the highlight
There isn't any real choice for coffee shops in t4 so it's that or pretty much nothing.
Price is too much the product was good. Had cookie drink and it was refreshing and nice. There was a robot to place your trash. It was cool.

Undrinkable coffee.  Paid $8.10 for  a cafe latte.  Milky, frothy yuck.  Completely undrinkable.  I asked for more coffee and to their credit they added a shot.  Don't waste your money on the coffee.  I threw 80% out after battling through a bit with an extra shot.  Not drinkable

eating here at 2am is so peaceful, cookie dough croissant and iced salted caramel latte perfect duo. might be too sweet for most of you guys, but once in a while have to get this duo. first time trying the croissant and its not too bad, not too sweet for me.

Visited on new year’s evening… Wonderful experience. Had a skim milk flat white that was delicious. Most importantly service here excellent. Staff wearing black headwear took our order and made me and my sister’s drinks, and she was so friendly. Respectful young lady who makes wonderful quality drinks. Bravo.
